Summary: strange bash/white square object that skipped through the sky followed by 2 chinook helicopters
divs: sighting detailsokay here goes....it was just getting dark and went in my back yard b\c i took my dogs out.i noticed 2 chinook helicopters with their lights on(1 in front of the other but diagonally),it didn't even phase me b\c they always fly over my house,i guess my house is in their flight path...well anyway i started to go in the house when i noticed something strange...it was bash or white,something dark or brown was on the middle of the craft,maybe an ensigna or a dark window but something,it was square,no mistake it was light enough for me to see that...it made no noise,just the chinooks did,the square object skipped through the air..well this is what it did....stop,go,stop,go,stop,go...but really fast but slow enough that you could tell it was a stop,go movement....i usually bring my camera outside to film things but not this time,so i yelled for the camera b\c i didn't want to miss anything but my g\f brought it out too late....now this is what i saw...when it passed over my house it went in the direction of the sun going down so i kind of watched it get just outside of tucson and it went to the west and the chinooks went to the northwest towards ryan airfield...oh i forget..it didn't have any lights on it,nothing was lit up
